""Superstore Sales Analysis & Forecasting""

-Project Overview
    This project presents an end-to-end data analytics and machine learning workflow built on a retail Superstore sales dataset. The objective was to clean and analyze transactional sales data, build an interactive business dashboard, and apply a lightweight machine learning model to forecast future sales trends.

    The project demonstrates the complete lifecycle of a data project — from raw data handling to insights, visualization, and predictive modeling.

-Dataset
    Source: Kaggle – Superstore Sales Dataset
    Type: Transactional retail sales data
    Granularity: Order-level data aggregated to monthly level for forecasting

